Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.85,0:23:19.15,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}I'm close to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.80,0:23:25.30,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}永遠在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:30.46,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}即便是看不見明天的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.10,0:23:36.55,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}也會用心靈呼喚你
